{"tid":2040821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：中美「香港戰役」已經打響","createTime":"2020-05-28T23:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T03:11:12.000Z","uid":125168,"like":82,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"2d42a7b3bfcae1396cba507c2959030695f6f8ab","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:47:36.000Z","msg":"環球時報：中美「香港戰役」已經打響<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392592&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=aed3ea93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392592&h=0624d953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392592</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地《環球時報》發表社評，指中美之間的「香港戰役」已經打響。<br />\n<br />\n社評指，中美「香港戰役」總態勢由中國掌握實際主動權，通過國安法後，將大大壓縮美國干預香港局勢的能力，而香港將來的道路和繁榮，將會由香港人在國家幫助下獨立塑造。<br />\n<br />\n社評又指，雖然美國氣勢洶洶，但可以對全局性產生影響的實質手段其實只有一個，就是取消香港的獨立關稅地位，將香港當成中國內地對待，然而這是一把雙刃劍，同時會打擊大量美國公司，嚴重影響美國對香港的出口。<br />\n<br />\n通過國安法，加上美國的錯誤行動，將會重構香港的輿論氛圍，賣國主義將逐漸失去在香港囂張作亂的空間，香港最終將穩定下來，繼續扮演金融中心的角色，開闢廣闊前景。"},{"pid":"b9d0ed3afdfb61187eca95636235cec702930497","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:48:26.000Z","msg":"貿易戰最後咪又係跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7677f79de5937a500623f5652aa1b803f297d0","tid":2040821,"uid":19552,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:14.000Z","msg":"呢個胡錫進根本係現代義和團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb196e714f21b71121e41f71acda5037730d7ef3","tid":2040821,"uid":2054,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:23.000Z","msg":"全面小腔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0148c50d6c5f1c69cc2c4874c6b7318b29341a57","tid":2040821,"uid":350216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國社評"},{"pid":"edb9dc7cb80d9c54141ac85668c741c96b256719","tid":2040821,"uid":131188,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"而香港將來的道路和繁榮，將會由香港人在國家幫助下<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立</span></strong>塑造<br />\n環球時報咁大膽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f7c947612b12aa61c3554161323400b988f641","tid":2040821,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:50:12.000Z","msg":"歐洲今次因為疫情，導致經濟衰退<br />\n<br />\n所以一定會奶共，中共覺得贏面大"},{"pid":"1f83bc5b75f7a922e06af4225ce17d4f6ea8cfe5","tid":2040821,"uid":192824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:50:17.000Z","msg":"食屎啦胡尻"},{"pid":"dbe3e79b259e9bacab0ef0a4d05fd04c4b315135","tid":2040821,"uid":253040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將香港當成中國內地對待，然而這是一把雙刃劍，同時會打擊大量美國公司，嚴重影響美國對香港的出口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將香港當成中國內地對待，佢哋又唔開心？"},{"pid":"5eb378044085017d9279fc1cd9166c58d154c47d","tid":2040821,"uid":5502,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"edb9dc7cb80d9c54141ac85668c741c96b256719","tid":2040821,"uid":131188,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"而香港將來的道路和繁榮，將會由香港人在國家幫助下<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立</span></strong>塑造<br />\n環球時報咁大膽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\