/strong>"},{"pid":"59b6bfaca8544bf3d637c8a1c4308a7310fdbb16","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c489c63240c281e9f6f08210c6d498b6fe8c775","tid":2040821,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:57:29.000Z","msg":"係咪即係宣戰？"},{"pid":"1e001d7ad37a75061e038a3e300dfadf85d3148d","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:58:24.000Z","msg":"庫德洛︰如有需要會將對香港與中國的待遇看齊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392593&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=218bc580\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392593&h=be98be36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392593</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普表示，他對中國近日行為感到不滿，將在當地周五公布涉及中國的新政策。白宮經濟顧問庫德洛指，北京通過建立港區國安法是犯下了巨大錯誤，指華府不能袖手旁觀。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普對記者表示，會在周五召開記者會公布針對中國的新政策。特朗普沒說明新政策是否回應北京通過建立港區國安法。<br />\n<br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛接受電視訪問時形容，中國通過建立港區國安法是掠奪香港的自由，犯下了巨大錯誤，華府不能袖手旁觀，北京必須為此負責。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛又表示，美國如有需要會將對香港的待遇與對中國的待遇看齊，屆時將為公司在香港上市及關稅等事項帶來影響。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院議長佩洛西則表示，國際社會應齊聲反對中國通過建立港區國安法，又指特朗普可以根據《香港人權及民主法案》採取一系列措施回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康則指，中國通過香港國安法將令中國國安部可以在香港執法，又形容國安部如同蘇聯時代的秘密警察，以酷刑及脅迫著稱。<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文表示，如果中國不撤回香港國安法，倫敦政府不排除更改英國國民(海外)護照，即BNO持有人的入境待遇，由免簽證入境六個月改為容許持證者在英國工作及學習十二個月，長遠可以作為進一步申請公民資格的途徑。<br />\n<br />\n有關注香港事務的保守黨國會議員指，藍韜文的聲明是個好開始，但期望當局採取更多措施，包括加快BNO持有人取得英國公民資格的程序。"},{"pid":"f3298f01f7ebeddd1ade00ce79751dbdf6d0b868","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c489c63240c281e9f6f08210c6d498b6fe8c775","tid":2040821,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:57:29.000Z","msg":"係咪即係宣戰？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:58:44.000Z","msg":"其實已經無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd6e31c09a364a33ee4bc9d69fdedfaef9ed0d6","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab4311036d208abd1402bccfabe8922ddcdd3b8","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee21b53f541bcd9cfa3c2e3a8db9d95955e7bcf","tid":2040821,"uid":88982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:01:37.000Z","msg":"黎啦隻癲狗吠得愈大聲愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9172eaf2df5acab3cda847ce6c5a59ca78469389","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8782077ec636d22ed24acf936337e2004c23e1","tid":2040821,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9d3c9d8c5cdb321c23350fd4f51a40473ae982","tid":2040821,"uid":47202,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:05:31.000Z","msg":"繼續將香港上升到中美戰爭級別就啱，千祈唔好縮，中國最好有咁串得咁串，大肆宣佈香港戰爭勝利，等侵想放軟手腳都難。"},{"pid":"b66cdc60bd928eec11297a11f78708a7c46975b0","tid":2040821,"uid":18477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5eb378044085017d9279fc1cd9166c58d154c47d","tid":2040821,"uid":5502,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"edb9dc7cb80d9c54141ac85668c741c96b256719","tid":2040821,"uid":131188,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"而香港將來的道路和繁榮，將會